de>itemprop</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/itemref\"><code>itemref</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/itemscope\"><code>itemscope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/itemtype\"><code>itemtype</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/lang\"><code>lang</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/nonce\"><code>nonce</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/part\"><code>part</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/slot\"><code>slot</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/spellcheck\"><code>spellcheck</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/style\"><code>style</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/tabindex\"><code>tabindex</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/title\"><code>title</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/translate\"><code>translate</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/x-ms-acceleratorkey\"><code>x-ms-acceleratorkey</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/x-ms-format-detection\"><code>x-ms-format-detection</code></a></li></ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details>\n      <summary><code>&lt;input&gt;</code> types</summary>\n      <ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/button\"><code>&lt;input type=\"button\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/checkbox\"><code>&lt;input type=\"checkbox\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/color\"><code>&lt;input type=\"color\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/date\"><code>&lt;input type=\"date\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/datetime-local\"><code>&lt;input type=\"datetime-local\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/email\"><code>&lt;input type=\"email\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/file\"><code>&lt;input type=\"file\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/hidden\"><code>&lt;input type=\"hidden\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/image\"><code>&lt;input type=\"image\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/month\"><code>&lt;input type=\"month\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/number\"><code>&lt;input type=\"number\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/password\"><code>&lt;input type=\"password\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/radio\"><code>&lt;input type=\"radio\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/range\"><code>&lt;input type=\"range\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/reset\"><code>&lt;input type=\"reset\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/search\"><code>&lt;input type=\"search\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/submit\"><code>&lt;input type=\"submit\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/tel\"><code>&lt;input type=\"tel\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/text\"><code>&lt;input type=\"text\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/time\"><code>&lt;input type=\"time\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/url\"><code>&lt;input type=\"url\"&gt;</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/week\"><code>&lt;input type=\"week\"&gt;</code></a></li></ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/MDN\">Documentation:</a></strong></li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details>\n      <summary>Useful lists</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Index\">All pages index</a></li>\n      </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details>\n      <summary>Contribute</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/MDN\">The MDN project</a></li>\n      </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html_elemente","title":"HTML Elemente","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In dieser Liste sind alle HTML-Elemente aufgelistet, die in HTML5 oder vorherigen Versionen spezifiziert wurden. Wenn die Elemente in spitzen Klammern eingeschlossen sind, sind es HTML-Tags (<code>&lt;elementenname&gt;</code>). Elemente sind \"Entities\", die spezifizieren, wie das HTML-Dokument aufgebaut ist. Außerdem bestimmen sie, welcher Inhaltstyp in welchem Teil des HTML-Dokuments eingefügt werden sollte.</p>\n\n<p>Diese Seite listet alle aktuellen Standard-HTML-Tags auf,&nbsp;aber auch obsolete. Elemente, die erst in HTML5 eingeführt wurden,&nbsp;werden referenziert, wobei die anderen Elemente in HTML5 auch gültig sind.</p>\n\n<p>In HTML wird ein Element über das Start-Tag definiert und wenn das Element&nbsp;weiteren Inhalt enthält, wird ein Ende-Tag angefügt, das einen Slash <code>&lt;/elementenname&gt;</code> beinhaltet. Einige Elemente müssen nicht geschlossen werden, wie z.B. das <code>&lt;img&gt;</code>-Tag. Diese Elemente werden auch void-Elemente genannt. Das HTML–Dokument besteht aus beliebig vielen Elementen, wobei diese Struktur der Elemente als Baum bezeichnet wird. Jedes Element repräsentiert den Inhalt über den Tag-Namen. So repräsentiert das <code>&lt;title&gt;</code>-Element den Titel des Dokuments. Weitere Elemente finden sie in der Liste.</p>\n\n<p>Die Elemente, die mit dem&nbsp; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/HTML5\"><img alt=\"This element has been added in HTML5\" src=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/files/3843/HTML5_Badge_32.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"This element has been added in HTML5\" loading=\"lazy\"></a>&nbsp; Symbol gekennzeichnet sind, wurden in HTML5 eingeführt. Einige hier gelistete Elemente&nbsp;wurden in der HTML5 Spezifikation erweitert oder modifiziert. Elemente, die veraltet oder keine Standardelemente sind, sind ausgegraut. Es wird davon abgeraten diese Elemente in neuen Webseiten zu benutzen und sie sollten von existierenden Seiten entfernt werden, um unerwünschtes Verhalten zu vermeiden.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Das Symbol kennzeichnet die Elemente, die in <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/components-intro/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Components collection of specifications </a>definiert wurden.</p>\n\n<div class=\"index widgeted\" id=\"sect2\"><span id=\"A\">A</span>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/acronym\"><code>&lt;acronym&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><s class=\"deprecatedElement obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/applet\"><code>&lt;applet&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/area\"><code>&lt;area&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n<span id=\"B\">B</span>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/b\"><code>&lt;b&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/base\"><code>&lt;base&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><s class=\"deprecatedElement obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Fonts\"><code>&lt;basefont&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdi\"><code>&lt;bdi&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdo\"><code>&lt;bdo&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bgsound\"><code>&lt;bgsound&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/big\"><code>&lt;big&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blink\"><code>&lt;blink&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blockquote\"><code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/br\"><code>&lt;br&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n<span id=\"C\">C</span>\n\n<ul>\n <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/caption\"><code>&lt;caption&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><s class=\"deprecatedElement obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/center\"><code>&lt;center&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\"><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/code\"><code>&lt;code&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/col\"><code>&lt;col&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/colgroup\"><code>&lt;colgroup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li class=\"webcomp\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/content\"><code>&lt;content&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li></li>\n</ul>\n<span id=\"D\">D</span>\n\n<ul>\n <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/data\"><code>&lt;data&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/datalist\"><code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dd\"><code>&lt;dd&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li class=\"webcomp\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>&lt;decorator&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/del\"><code>&lt;del&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><s class=\"deprecatedElement obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dir\"><code>&lt;dir&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dl\"><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dt\"><code>&lt;dt&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n<span id=\"E\">E</span>\n\n<ul>\n <li class=\"webcomp\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>&lt;element&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\